      <title>Adobe 股价下跌，因预测疲弱，粉丝担心竞争和人工智能工作</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/adobe-drops-weak-forecast-fans-worries-about-competition-ai-efforts-2024-03-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adobe 股价周五下跌 12%，原因是该公司黯淡的季度预测引发了人们对激烈竞争的担忧，并使那些希望通过生成式 AI 集成提振的投资者感到失望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/adobe-drops-weak-forecast-fans-worries-about-competition-ai-efforts-2024-03-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 11:24:52 GMT</pubDate>
